data.description:
Come see this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style home with three car garage located in a growing neighborhood!  This home offers a large foyer and vaulted ceilings in the great room and master bedroom! The open kitchen has granite counter tops, 42 inch soft close maple kitchen cabinets, and all stainless steel appliances! Master Suite with a large walk in closet,  luxury bath with jetted tub, separate shower and adult height, double bowl marble vanity! You will also notice the 4 inch trim and rounded corners throughout! The large, unfinished basement also offers a egress window and rough in for a future bathroom! With this house under two years young, you will not want to miss out on making it your future home!

Showing by appointment only. Please call 314-650-2071 or email krijoh06@gmail.com.
